dc_title_s: Meiji kaisei Tōkyō zenzu Sagano Hikotarō.
dc_description_s: Copperplate print. In Japanese. Oriented with north to the upper right. Relief shown by hachures. Includes address charts by ward (ku), guide for tourists, time table, and legend. Shows views of tourist attractions. Inset: Yokohama shigaizu 2 sheets joined. 1 map: col.; 46 x 66 cm., folded to 18 x 10 cm.
